---
description: Flask API conventions for xastrinxop-api
globs: "xastrinxop-api/**/*.py"
alwaysApply: false
---

- App factory and routes live under `xastrinxop-api/src/xastrinxop_api/`.
- Add/extend tests in `xastrinxop-api/tests/test_api.py` using the existing `_login` helper.
- Run `make test-api` before claiming done.
